{"tid":1069442,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"權威評歐洲賽季最佳陣：美斯C.朗領銜","createTime":"2019-03-20T03:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T09:06:17.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"31476dc4caac8e37c85ff8155c7644c4c3342899","tid":1069442,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:41:52.000Z","msg":"媒體評歐洲賽季至今的最佳陣<br />\n<br />\n  隨著國家隊比賽週的到來，五大聯賽也暫時告一段落。數據網站whoscored則統計出了今季至今的五大聯賽最佳陣容，美斯和C.朗拿度不出意外地入圍。<br />\n<br />\n  在這套陣容中，德甲和法甲各3人，英超、意甲各2人，西甲僅有美斯入圍，不過後者的8.6分也是所有球員里場均評分最高的。<br />\n<br />\n  陣型：442<br />\n<br />\n  門將：W-賓尼迪斯（尼斯，7.1分）<br />\n<br />\n  後衛：甘美治（拜仁，7.4分）、雲迪積克（利物浦，7.4分）、奧爾班（萊比錫，7.5分）、侯斯頓保（萊比錫，7.6分）<br />\n<br />\n  中場：美斯（巴塞，8.6分）、薩瓦尼耶（尼姆，7.9分）、亞曆杭德羅-高美斯（阿特蘭大，7.5分）、史達寧（曼城，7.7分）<br />\n<br />\n  前鋒：麥巴比（巴黎，8.1分）、C.朗拿度（祖記，7.8分）"},{"pid":"e6fc149eef634ff205865d3d9a78bff1ac301a51","tid":1069442,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:43:54.000Z","msg":"尼馬?"},{"pid":"7ff204c5261098b86ef56b9449ec851f5d59d25b","tid":1069442,"uid":173952,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"原來美斯係中場"},{"pid":"303838f67695150747dbf58b9da2b92a501729bf","tid":1069442,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">甘美治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界杯輸佢幾球"},{"pid":"8d69e570142a5a23aede297ef78f11143ae2f895","tid":1069442,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"A.高美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0886cfc47a5768fc460df9c9fcb661d271f55779","tid":1069442,"uid":211579,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"史達寧（曼城... <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" cl